	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott mitt sinen gnaden mitt uns.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Des brieffs halb ist nitt redlich gehandlet und one valsch nitt zuͦgangen; yedoch fröwt mich, das, der inn uff gebrochen, nuͤt, das üch oder mir schaden möge, funden hatt.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Den brieff hab ich junkher <persName type="auto_name">Hansen Buttlern</persName>, minem gevattern, gäben, weiß nitt, wie er inn versorget; doch hab ich inn beschickt und imm den brieff vorgeläsen, daruff er hingadt, die sach ze erfaren, da er üch wol wirt berichten; ich wöllte uff die sach nitt vil setzen etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Supplicium et confessionem Pythonicae cupio scire avidissime; res est enim nostro saeculo rari exempli.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quam cuperem <persName type="auto_name">Christophorum</persName> obtinere posse ducatum Wirtenbergensem, sed vereor harpyas <placeName type="auto_name">Austriacas</placeName> et Hispanicas; caeterum vivit deus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi, quas a <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculo</persName> literas mittis; quas vicissim ab ipso accepi, imo quas ultimo scriptas accepi, tecum communico, ut sequenti remittas septimana.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Describere nihil potui.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam vera sint, quae de Magdeburg[ensibus] accepit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="auto_name">Anglia</placeName> literas 20. octobris scriptas et ex <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> 21. novembris editas accepi hoc mense.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cursus verbi dei non impeditur in <placeName type="auto_name">Anglia</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1560" cert="high">Hopperus</persName> noster recte habet et fortiter se gerit; opponit se ipsi episcopus <placeName ref="l296" cert="high">Londoniensis</placeName>, qui cupit illum onerare nescio quibus ceremoniis.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1560" cert="high">Hopperus</persName> post manuum impositionem ab apostolis traditam nihil in inauguratione sustinet imponi.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Lis sub iudice vertitur.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alioqui in <placeName type="auto_name">Anglia</placeName> fit, quod alibi; plurimi libertatem carnis praetexunt licentiae carnis; sed hi sunt mores extremi saeculi.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam mox veniat dominus iudicare vivos et mortuos.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Optima quaeque sperantur in <placeName type="auto_name">Anglia</placeName>; rex crescit et aetate et moribus sanctis; dominus concedat ei, ut perseveret, ne Ioae vestigia insistat.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, amicissime frater, et frequentius scribe.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui fit, quod tantum est de Caesare silentium?</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Puto vana esse, quae sparsa sunt de Sch[w]endio colligente militem.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">5. decembris 1550.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">B[ullingerus]</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Sinem lieben herren und bruͦder m. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosien Blaureren</persName>, whonhafft zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Wintherdur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
